<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend::loadFile() method does not return the include() and include_once() return values. It could be handy in some cases.</p>

<p>To implement this, just modify the lines 202 to 206 of the Zend.php file from :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if ($once) {
    include_once($filespec);
} else {
    include($filespec);
}
</code></pre>

<p>to :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if ($once) {
    return include_once($filespec);
} else {
    return include($filespec);
}
</code></pre>

